- Ayo. Buka pintunya!

17
00:01:29,095 --> 00:01:30,138
Aku permisi, Pak.

18
00:01:37,937 --> 00:01:39,105
Ayah bilang, buka pintu.

19
00:02:05,757 --> 00:02:06,925
Ayo duduklah.

20
